<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/854677-so-is-anyone-else-confused-by-fielding-s">So, is anyone else confused by Fielding&#39;s current age and what year it must be? It seems like in the &quot;present&quot; when he is telling the story, he is in his 80s. If he was 13 years old in 1984, then the &quot;present&quot; would actually be sometime in the 2050s. Is that correct? Yet when he was in the &quot;present&quot;, it did not seem futuristic or any different than 1984. Am I missing something there?</a>
</div>
