<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I actually skyped with Tiffany, the author of the book this Friday. When Fielding is talking it is in the future. But that wasn&apos;t important to the sto<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I actually skyped with Tiffany, the author of the book this Friday. When Fielding is talking it is in the future. But that wasn't important to the story so she didn't go into detail about technology and all the futuristic things that go along with that.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
