        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1916885511" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14585436171791953641">I really really loved this book. I know people didn&apos;t like the metaphorical writing but I always have been a sucker for poetic writing. I like when books make me question the way I think about things and I enjoy symbolism and when things are woven so intricately with the plot line. Like the story is just so well woven and elegant and the author just expressed things so eloquently. It all just fit together so perfectly and I really felt affected when reading the book. Definitely a favorite.</span>
  <span id="freeText14585436171791953641" style="display:none">I really really loved this book. I know people didn't like the metaphorical writing but I always have been a sucker for poetic writing. I like when books make me question the way I think about things and I enjoy symbolism and when things are woven so intricately with the plot line. Like the story is just so well woven and elegant and the author just expressed things so eloquently. It all just fit together so perfectly and I really felt affected when reading the book. Definitely a favorite.</span>
